HEADWORD: Signboard
<hw>Sign"board`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A board, placed on
or before a shop, office, etc., on which some notice is given, as the
name of a firm, of a business, or the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

